1. basic functions:
get   /                   static   show main page
get   /login              static   show login/signup page
post  /login              dynamic  perform login action
post  /signup             dynamic  perform signup action
post  /logout             dynamic  perform logout action
post  /msg                dynamic  send messages to others
get   /friendlist         dynamic  get friend list
get   /hello              dynamic  long polling request


2. advanced functions:
get   /userlist           dynamic  get all user's list

put   /friendrequest      dynamic  request friendship with a user
put   /friendrefuse       dynamic  refuse to become friend with request user
put   /friendconfirm      dynamic  confirm friendship with request user

put   /dropblack          dynamic  drop one friend/user into black list

post  /filemsg            dynamic  upload one file as a message
